{"tid":2235115,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【夥警行動】重組飛行服務隊近 800 次航程 8.23 飛行路徑明顯異常 疑監視 12 港人快艇","createTime":"2020-10-08T11:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T16:56:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf1181d392cc4b342db7f1d410f54a353654903","tid":2235115,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"12 港人 8 月 23 日「被送中」當日，兩架政府飛行服務隊（GFS）飛機被揭曾出動，令人關注警方是否一直監視港人。「12 港人關注組」今日再披露 GFS 內部紀錄，顯示兩飛機當日航程均屬「警方行動（P-OPS）」，要求港府交代警員是否一直監視快艇。<br />\n<br />\n內部紀錄顯示，GFS 8.23 當日以 H175 獵豹直升機，以及「龐巴迪挑戰者 605」定翼機，支援警方執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》透過航空雷達公司，翻查 GFS 全部 9 架同款的直升機及定翼機，最近 3 個月合共 761 次飛行紀錄，發現 8 月 23 日出動的兩架飛機，航程與機隊往常路徑明顯不同，亦與載有 12 港人快艇當日預計路線重叠；而近三個月航程紀錄顯示，除了 8.23 當日，定翼機從未在凌晨時份出動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《蘋果日報》今日引述消息報道，有警員當日在兩機上，全程監視 12 港人快艇被截獲的過程。惟警方未回應是否屬實，僅重申其與行動無關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A5%E8%AD%A6%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%E8%BF%91-800-%E6%AC%A1%E8%88%AA%E7%A8%8B-8-23-%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%91%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E7%95%B0%E5%B8%B8-%E7%96%91%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96-12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%AB%E8%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25BF%2591-800-%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A8%258B-8-23-%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25BE%2591%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%25B8%25B8-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596-12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%2589%2587%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrwTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=3e616979\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25BF%2591-800-%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A8%258B-8-23-%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25BE%2591%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%25B8%25B8-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596-12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%2589%2587%2F&h=175c728b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A5%E8%AD%A6%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%E8%BF%91-800-%E6%AC%A1%E8%88%AA%E7%A8%8B-8-23-%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%91%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E7%95%B0%E5%B8%B8-%E7%96%91%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96-12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%AB%E8%89%87/</a>"},{"pid":"ce02b6246e55effd66900e0abb25c4f38bb7e592","tid":2235115,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"獵豹直升機多數在港執勤 僅 7 次遠離港水域 8.23 航程最遠<br />\n<img src=\"https://interactive.thestandnews.com/2020/10/12-people-flights-2/map-blvh-1200.jpg?rpwcMqTGeD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finteractive.thestandnews.com%2F2020%2F10%2F12-people-flights-2%2Fmap-blvh-1200.jpg%3FrpwcMqTGeD&h=0fd469b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGFS 目前有 7 架獵豹直升機， 7 月 7 日至 10 月 8 日期間共 475 次的航行紀錄顯示，絕大多數時間都在香港特區範圍內出勤，其中只有 7 次飛至距離香港水域東南方較遠的位置。<br />\n<br />\n8 月 23 日當日，編號 B-LVH 的獵豹直升機飛至香港水域界限以外 26 海浬，是近 3 個月離港最遠的一次任務。<br />\n<br />\n定翼機最近 3 個月 除 8.23 外從未凌晨出動<br />\n<br />\n翻查紀錄，GFS現時有兩架挑戰者605定翼機，由 7 月 8 日至 10 月 8 日兩飛機共 286 次航行紀錄，幾乎全部於早上及下午出勤，唯獨 8 月 23 日曾於凌晨出動，是近 3 個月內唯一一次。至於獵豹直升機，則共有 6 次在早上 6 時前出動。"},{"pid":"4cd6d1e83ff00a380814f263f8a3d4295e1c3f7f","tid":2235115,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daadf7fb92b98c5bfcf70a24c6056e952e77f020","tid":2235115,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cd6d1e83ff00a380814f263f8a3d4295e1c3f7f","tid":2235115,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f45e03c3728331520cdda6f55b73c160fde9116","tid":2235115,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e787b046bd471f1fa4946aabb07111cabcff6cd","tid":2235115,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528189-20200525.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528189-20200525.htm&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrwTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=01e84b3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528189-20200525.htm&h=44e83651\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528189-20200525.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">飛行服務隊表態支持「港區國安法」決定 稱已作好準備</span></span></strong><br />\n2020-05-25 HKT 13:36<br />\n<br />\n多個紀律部隊首長陸續表態，支持全國人大將審議建立健全香港特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的決定。<br />\n<br />\n政府飛行服務隊總監胡偉雄表示支持決定，全力支持特區政府履行應有職責，竭力維護國家安全，政府飛行服務隊已作好準備，支持警方果斷執法，會全力支持特區政府推行草案，建立安全及穩定社會，確保香港長期繁榮穩定，長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n胡偉雄表示，過去一年香港出現的暴力不斷升級，巿民的生命財產受到越來越大的威脅及破壞，恐怖主義亦正在港滋生，危害國家安全的活動更越趨猖獗，令社會充斥暴力，失去安寧。"},{"pid":"d7a754fed9e0b3559805e29bccd03e0fd0200425","tid":2235115,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc6612b8e6950d786c846b5a12820ff51ad345e","tid":2235115,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81320a0f9bf91f18bdb54b3f07213f423b82fc5","tid":2235115,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2e5e1d4a2d066ca6102932012c7d80658549a4","tid":2235115,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81320a0f9bf91f18bdb54b3f07213f423b82fc5","tid":2235115,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a